Name:Cupid
Desc:The Cupid only wakes up on the first night. They must choose another player to be their lover, their lover is then woken up. Cupid and their lover must win the game together. They may win with the townsfolk, but if their lover is not a townsfolk, then they can only win if all other players are dead. If the Cupid dies, they take their lover with them and vice versa.
Card:The Cupid wakes up in first night, choosing another player to be their lover, who is then woken up. They must win together. If the Cupid dies, they take their lover with them and vice versa.
